snippet: The evidence in the Seminole County case of Clemente Javier Aguirre points to a family member of the victims, lawyers say.
abstract: Lawyers for Florida inmate Clemente Javier Aguirre say DNA evidence clears him of fatal stabbings of two women, seven years after he was sentenced to death for crime.
lead_paragraph: The evidence in the Seminole County case of Clemente Javier Aguirre points to a family member of the victims, lawyers say.

headline.seo: Lawyers Say DNA Clears Florida Inmate in Killings
headline.main: Lawyers Say DNA Clears Florida Inmate in Two Killings
headline.print_headline: Lawyers Say DNA Clears Florida Inmate in Two Killings
